name: Manifested Skull Archfiend
desc:
"Summoned Skull" + 1 DARK monster
This card's name becomes "Summoned Skull" while it is on the field, but it is still treated as an "Archfiend" card. "Summoned Skull" you control gain 500 ATK. If this Fusion Summoned card you control is sent to your GY by your opponent's card: You can Special Summon 1 "Summoned Skull" from your hand, Deck, or GY.
